  "title": "Operations Executive- Ecommerce & Transportation",
  "description": "<p><strong>Companies:</strong> Friend of Bus Pte Ltd &amp; Retail Ministry<br>\n<strong>Location:</strong> WCEGA Tower@Bukit Batok<br>\n<strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-time</p>\n<h3><strong>About the Role</strong></h3>\n<p>We are looking for a versatile and responsible Operations Executive to support daily operational activities across our two business entities — Friend of Bus Pte Ltd, which specializes in private bus transportation, and Retail Ministry, our e-commerce arm.</p>\n<p>This position will primarily focus on operations and coordination, ensuring smooth execution of transport schedules, vehicle maintenance, regulatory renewals, and e-commerce order fulfilment.</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<h4><strong>Transport Operations (Friend of Bus Pte Ltd)</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee and plan bus scheduling for daily and chartered jobs.</li>\n  <li>Manage and coordinate subcontractor assignments for outsourced transport services.</li>\n  <li>Schedule and monitor regular maintenance for all company vehicles.</li>\n  <li>Handle the renewal of Vehicle Parking Certificates (VPC), Road Tax, and Insurance for all vehicles.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate operational and compliance records.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>E-commerce Operations (Retail Ministry)</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee the packing, labelling, and dispatching of online orders.</li>\n  <li>Ensure inventory control and stock accuracy, including restocking and product listing updates.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with logistics providers and monitor order delivery timelines.</li>\n  <li>Support daily operations to ensure efficient and timely order fulfilment.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>General Administrative Support</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain proper filing and documentation of operational activities.</li>\n  <li>Assist management in process improvements and other ad-hoc operational matters.</li>\n</ul>",
